headline: Combined Insurance Unveils New Chubb Benefits Brand
summary: Combined Insurance Company of America, a Chubb company and a leading North American provider of supplemental insurance, today announced the launch of the Chubb Benefits brand, which delivers greater clarity and consistency through closer alignment with the global Chubb brand.
